cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is about weakly supervised semantic image segmentation using neural networks and loss functions. The most relevant sub-category is likely cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), as the paper deals with image segmentation and analysis. Other likely sub-categories include cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), as the paper involves training neural networks and developing new loss functions for improved performance.
